1. FREE USAGE

PanelIyagi may be used free of charge for any purpose,
including personal, commercial, educational,
governmental, and organizational use.

---

2. REDISTRIBUTION AND DISTRIBUTION PLATFORMS

Redistribution of the original PanelIyagi binaries
is permitted worldwide.

PanelIyagi may be distributed through, including but not limited to:

• Linux distribution repositories
• Ubuntu Software Center and GNOME Software
• Snap Store, Flatpak repositories, AppImage mirrors
• Personal or commercial websites
• GitHub Releases and software mirrors
• Internal enterprise systems
• Linux distribution ISO images
• Physical storage media

No additional permission is required.

---

3. PACKAGING RIGHTS

Third parties, Linux distributions, and repository maintainers
are permitted to:

• Repackage PanelIyagi into distribution-specific formats
• Create installers or integration scripts
• Provide dependency handling
• Include PanelIyagi in bundled software collections

Provided that the distributed binaries are kept in their original, unmodified form.

Note: PanelIyagi core is provided as **binary-only software**;
no source code is included. Modification of the core is not possible.

